==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: fuck
<hw>fuck</hw> <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>to have sexual intercourse
(with).</def> <mark>[vulgar slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> love, make love, sleep with, get laid, have sex,
know, do it, be intimate, have intercourse, have it away, have it off,
screw, jazz, eff, have, hump, lie with, bed, have a go at it, get it on,
bonk.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

